{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "18", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "06", "M": "54", "S": "46"}}, "news": [{"title": "Sand shortage in Mangaluru adds \u20b92 lakh to cost of building a house", "para": "Mangaluru builders face a severe sand shortage, escalating construction costs by nearly Rs 2.25 lakh per standard house. A four-year ban on sand mining in CRZ areas forces contractors to use coarser, less ideal sand from non-CRZ regions, leading to significant wastage. This crisis is pushing up prices and impacting project budgets.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/building-costs-surge-by-225-lakh-due-to-sand-shortage-in-mangaluru/130346903?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-56288/130346903.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "MMRDA starts land acquisition for \u2018Third Mumbai\u2019; consent process from April 27", "para": "MMRDA has begun land acquisition for 'Third Mumbai,' the Karnala-Sai-Chirner New Town, spanning 124 villages in Raigad. Landowners can opt for monetary compensation or land-based returns, including a land pooling model. This initiative aims to boost regional economic growth and establish a major technology and infrastructure hub.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/mmrda-launches-land-acquisition-for-ambitious-third-mumbai-project/130346662?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-235538/130346662.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Over 900 acres of Mhada layouts will be redeveloped across Mumbai", "para": "Mhada is set to redevelop a dozen layouts spanning 923 acres, aiming to rehabilitate over 75,000 residents within 5-10 years. Key projects like Charkop and Gorai layouts will soon seek state cabinet approval. The initiative also includes slum rehabilitation and a push for rental housing under the state housing policy.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/mumbais-mhada-redevelopment-plan-923-acres-to-transform-housing-for-over-75000-residents/130346609?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-189645/130346609.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}